-- Saudi Basic Industries Corp. CEO Al-Mady Confirms Bond Size at $1 Billion
-- B y   I n a l   E r s a n
-- 2010-10-26T15:47:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-26/saudi-basic-industries-corp-ceo-al-mady-confirms-bond-size-at-1-billion.html
Saudi Basic Industries Corp. is
selling $1 billion of bonds, Chief Executive Officer Mohamed al-
Mady said in remarks to Al Arabiya television today.  The bonds will be priced around 165 basis points more than
the mid-swap rate, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
